All Implemented Interfaces:
Map<K,V>
public abstract class QueryResults<K,V,Q extends Query>
extends Object
implements Map<K,V>

Abstract class that can store that can store rows fetched by a Query. One object is created for each row fetched by the query. The value(Q q) method creates this object. The key(Q q) method creates the key that will be used to store the value object to the map.
